{"data":[{"name":"75:1","price":"1 J’en jure par le Jour de la résurrection !","arabic":"لَآ أُقۡسِمُ بِيَوۡمِ ٱلۡقِيَٰمَةِ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5552,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"75:2","price":"2 J’en jure par l’âme en proie aux remords[1513] !","arabic":"وَلَآ أُقۡسِمُ بِٱلنَّفۡسِ ٱللَّوَّامَةِ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5553,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"[1513] L’âme du croyant qui ne cesse de se reprocher ses manquements et ses péchés.","lang":"fr"},{"name":"75:3","price":"3 L’homme croit-il que Nous ne pourrons rassembler ses os ?","arabic":"أَيَحۡسَبُ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ أَلَّن نَّجۡمَعَ عِظَامَهُۥ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5554,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"75:4","price":"4 Nous pourrons au contraire reconstituer jusqu’à ses phalanges.","arabic":"بَلَىٰ قَٰدِرِينَ عَلَىٰٓ أَن نُّسَوِّيَ بَنَانَهُۥ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5555,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"75:5","price":"5 Mais l’homme aspire seulement à continuer à vivre dans le péché[1514].","arabic":"بَلۡ يُرِيدُ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ لِيَفۡجُرَ أَمَامَهُۥ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5556,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"[1514] En niant la Résurrection. ","lang":"fr"},{"name":"75:6","price":"6 Il demande : « Quand donc viendra le Jour de la résurrection ? »","arabic":"يَسۡـَٔلُ أَيَّانَ يَوۡمُ ٱلۡقِيَٰمَةِ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5557,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"75:7","price":"7 Lorsque les yeux seront exorbités,","arabic":"فَإِذَا بَرِقَ ٱلۡبَصَرُ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5558,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"75:8","price":"8 que la lune aura perdu toute clarté,","arabic":"وَخَسَفَ ٱلۡقَمَرُ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5559,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"75:9","price":"9 et que le soleil et la lune seront rassemblés[1515],","arabic":"وَجُمِعَ ٱلشَّمۡسُ وَٱلۡقَمَرُ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5560,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"[1515] Autre sens : se seront éteints.","lang":"fr"},{"name":"75:10","price":"10 l’homme, ce Jour-là, dira : « Où fuir ? »","arabic":"يَقُولُ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ يَوۡمَئِذٍ أَيۡنَ ٱلۡمَفَرُّ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5561,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"75:11","price":"11 Nulle part ! Il n’y aura, en effet, aucun refuge.","arabic":"كَلَّا لَا وَزَرَ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5562,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"75:12","price":"12 C’est à ton Seigneur, ce Jour-là, que tous feront retour.","arabic":"إِلَىٰ رَبِّكَ يَوۡمَئِذٍ ٱلۡمُسۡتَقَرُّ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5563,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"75:13","price":"13 L’homme sera, ce Jour-là, informé de ses actes les plus insignifiants.","arabic":"يُنَبَّؤُاْ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ يَوۡمَئِذِۭ بِمَا قَدَّمَ وَأَخَّرَ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5564,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"75:14","price":"14 Mais il sera lui-même parfaitement conscient de ses agissements,","arabic":"بَلِ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ عَلَىٰ نَفۡسِهِۦ بَصِيرَةٞ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5565,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"75:15","price":"15 quand bien même il invoquerait, pour se justifier, tous les arguments.","arabic":"وَلَوۡ أَلۡقَىٰ مَعَاذِيرَهُۥ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5566,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"75:16","price":"16 Ne répète pas avec empressement le Coran qui t’est révélé avant que sa récitation ne soit terminée[1516].","arabic":"لَا تُحَرِّكۡ بِهِۦ لِسَانَكَ لِتَعۡجَلَ بِهِۦٓ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5567,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"[1516] Voir note verset 114, sourate 20.","lang":"fr"},{"name":"75:17","price":"17 C’est à Nous qu’il revient de le fixer dans ta mémoire[1517] et de te le faire réciter.","arabic":"إِنَّ عَلَيۡنَا جَمۡعَهُۥ وَقُرۡءَانَهُۥ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5568,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"[1517] Littéralement : de le rassembler (dans ton cœur).","lang":"fr"},{"name":"75:18","price":"18 Lorsque Nous te le lisons[1518], contente-toi donc d’en suivre la récitation.","arabic":"فَإِذَا قَرَأۡنَٰهُ فَٱتَّبِعۡ قُرۡءَانَهُۥ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5569,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"[1518] Par l’intermédiaire de Gabriel.","lang":"fr"},{"name":"75:19","price":"19 C’est ensuite à Nous qu’il appartiendra d’en donner l’explication.","arabic":"ثُمَّ إِنَّ عَلَيۡنَا بَيَانَهُۥ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5570,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"75:20","price":"20 C’est que vous êtes obnubilés par ce bas bas-monde","arabic":"كَلَّا بَلۡ تُحِبُّونَ ٱلۡعَاجِلَةَ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5571,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"75:21","price":"21 au point d’en oublier totalement l’autre monde.","arabic":"وَتَذَرُونَ ٱلۡأٓخِرَةَ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5572,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"75:22","price":"22 Il y aura, ce Jour-là, des visages éclatants de beauté","arabic":"وُجُوهٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ نَّاضِرَةٌ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5573,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"75:23","price":"23 qui, vers leur Seigneur, seront résolument tournés[1519],","arabic":"إِلَىٰ رَبِّهَا نَاظِرَةٞ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5574,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"[1519] Contemplant Son Visage.","lang":"fr"},{"name":"75:24","price":"24 mais aussi des visages sombres et crispés,","arabic":"وَوُجُوهٞ يَوۡمَئِذِۭ بَاسِرَةٞ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5575,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"75:25","price":"25 persuadés de devoir subir une calamité.","arabic":"تَظُنُّ أَن يُفۡعَلَ بِهَا فَاقِرَةٞ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5576,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"75:26","price":"26 Lorsque l’âme du moribond remonte à la gorge,","arabic":"كَلَّآ إِذَا بَلَغَتِ ٱلتَّرَاقِيَ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5577,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"75:27","price":"27 et que ceux qui l’entourent demandent si quelqu’un peut le sauver,","arabic":"وَقِيلَ مَنۡۜ رَاقٖ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5578,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"75:28","price":"28 tandis que le mourant est convaincu qu’il va quitter ce monde,","arabic":"وَظَنَّ أَنَّهُ ٱلۡفِرَاقُ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5579,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"75:29","price":"29 et que, aux affres de la mort, s’ajoutent les affres de l’autre monde[1520],","arabic":"وَٱلۡتَفَّتِ ٱلسَّاقُ بِٱلسَّاقِ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5580,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"[1520] Autre sens : et que ses jambes sont nouées.","lang":"fr"},{"name":"75:30","price":"30 c’est vers ton Seigneur, ce jour-là, que l’âme du mourant est menée.","arabic":"إِلَىٰ رَبِّكَ يَوۡمَئِذٍ ٱلۡمَسَاقُ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5581,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"75:31","price":"31 Or, l’impie n’a ni cru, ni accompli la prière,","arabic":"فَلَا صَدَّقَ وَلَا صَلَّىٰ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5582,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"75:32","price":"32 mais a renié la vérité et s’est détourné de la foi,","arabic":"وَلَٰكِن كَذَّبَ وَتَوَلَّىٰ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5583,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"75:33","price":"33 puis s’est dirigé vers les siens en se pavanant.","arabic":"ثُمَّ ذَهَبَ إِلَىٰٓ أَهۡلِهِۦ يَتَمَطَّىٰٓ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5584,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"75:34","price":"34 « Malheur à toi, oui malheur ! »","arabic":"أَوۡلَىٰ لَكَ فَأَوۡلَىٰ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5585,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"75:35","price":"35 Encore une fois : « Malheur à toi, oui malheur ! »","arabic":"ثُمَّ أَوۡلَىٰ لَكَ فَأَوۡلَىٰٓ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5586,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"75:36","price":"36 L’homme croit-il qu’il ne sera ni ressuscité, ni jugé ?","arabic":"أَيَحۡسَبُ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ أَن يُتۡرَكَ سُدًى","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5587,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"75:37","price":"37 Ne tire-t-il pas son origine d’un liquide insignifiant répandu[1521],","arabic":"أَلَمۡ يَكُ نُطۡفَةٗ مِّن مَّنِيّٖ يُمۡنَىٰ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5588,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"[1521] Dans la matrice de la femme.","lang":"fr"},{"name":"75:38","price":"38 puis d’un corps s’accrochant à la matrice, avant qu’Allah ne lui donne la vie et n’en fasse un être accompli, ","arabic":"ثُمَّ كَانَ عَلَقَةٗ فَخَلَقَ فَسَوَّىٰ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5589,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"75:39","price":"39 de sexe masculin ou féminin ?","arabic":"فَجَعَلَ مِنۡهُ ٱلزَّوۡجَيۡنِ ٱلذَّكَرَ وَٱلۡأُنثَىٰٓ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5590,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"75:40","price":"40 Celui qui a pu créer cet être n’est-Il pas capable de ressusciter les morts ?!","arabic":"أَلَيۡسَ ذَٰلِكَ بِقَٰدِرٍ عَلَىٰٓ أَن يُحۡـِۧيَ ٱلۡمَوۡتَىٰ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5591,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"}],"chapter":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah","Chapter Al-Qiyamah","Qiyamah","Surah Qiyamah","Chapter Qiyamah","Al Qiyamah","Surah Al Qiyamah","Chapter Al Qiyamah","Surah 75","Chapter 75","The Resurrection","القيامة"]}